ActNational Defence Act
PrecisAppointment of PIERRE DAIGLE of Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec, to the position of special adviser to the Minister of National Defence, as Ombudsperson for the Department of National Defence and the Canadian Forces, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective February 23, 2009.
